casebody.data:
DeWitt C. Weeks, et al., Respondents v. William McCarty Little, Appellant. Decided June 23, 1887. Appeal from judgment entered in favor of plaintiffs against defendant. Jackson & Ingraham, for appellant. R. W. De Forest, for respondents.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., Truax and Dugro, JJ.

Per Curiam.

The judgment should be affirmed on the opinion of the referee.
